Install : pip install docker 
create new_image using Dockerfile attached

 
make sure all the files are in the same folder
Edit the user input in connmat.txt file
auto.py would create the leaf spine topology
Please give the input as <conatiner 1 name> <conatiner 2 name> <network type>
acceptabe network types are : bridge,L3,gre,vxlan
all the subnets used are in 30.0.0.0-49.0.0.0 range. Please make sure that you dont have any running bridge in the same range
run connectivity.yml file
